  <h>faigh</h>
  <p><g>faigh</g>
    <en>get</en> is an irregular verb.</p>
  <section id="forms">
    <h>forms</h>
    <p>The principal parts of <g>faigh</g> are – <ul>
        <li><m>gheibh</m> – future independent, i.e. <en>will get</en></li>
        <li><m>fhuair</m> – past independent, i.e. <en>got</en></li>
        <li><m>faighinn</m> – verbal noun, i.e. <en>getting</en></li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <section>
      <h>tense</h>
      <p><ul>
          <li>past <ul id="past">
              <li>active <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>fhuair</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>fhuair</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>do fhuair</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>passive <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>fhuaras</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>fhuaras</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>do fhuaras</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>future <ul id="future">
              <li>active <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>gheibh</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>gheibh</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhaigh</m>, am <m>faigh</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>passive <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>gheibhear</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>gheibhear</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhaighear</m>, am <m>faighear</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>conditional <ul id="conditional">
              <li>active <ul>
                  <li>first person singular <ul>
                      <li>independent – <m>gheibhinn</m></li>
                      <li>relative – a <m>gheibhinn</m></li>
                      <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhaighinn</m>, am <m>faighinn</m></li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>
                  <li>first person plural <ul>
                      <li>independent – <m>gheibheamaid</m></li>
                      <li>relative – a <m>gheibheamaid</m></li>
                      <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhaigheamaid</m>, am <m>faigheamaid</m></li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>
                  <li>second/third persons <ul>
                      <li>independent – <m>gheibheadh</m></li>
                      <li>relative – a <m>gheibheadh</m></li>
                      <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhaigheadh</m>, am <m>faigheadh</m></li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>passive <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>gheibhte</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>gheibhte</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhaighte</m>, am <m>faighte</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </section>
